<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{pageTitle}} - MediCare+</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex bg-slate-50">
  {{> common/sidebar-admin}}

  <div class="main-content flex-1 flex flex-col ml-64">
    {{> common/header-staff}}

    <main class="flex-1 p-8">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a
              href="/admin/department/list"
              class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 hover:bg-white rounded-xl border border-transparent hover:border-slate-200 hover:shadow-sm transition-all"
            >
              <i data-feather="arrow-left" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            </a>

            <div>
              <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">{{pageTitle}}</h1>
              <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">진료과 기본 정보와 운영 상태를 관리합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <span class="{{model.activeBadgeClass}}">{{model.activeText}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        {{#successMessage}}
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-green-200 bg-green-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-green-700">
            {{successMessage}}
          </div>
        {{/successMessage}}

        {{#errorMessage}}
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-red-200 bg-red-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-red-700">
            {{errorMessage}}
          </div>
        {{/errorMessage}}

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <aside class="lg:col-span-1 space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h2 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">요약 정보</h2>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
                  <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">진료과 ID</span>
                  <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">{{model.departmentId}}</span>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
                  <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">현재 상태</span>
                  <span class="{{model.activeBadgeClass}}">{{model.activeText}}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-indigo-600 rounded-2xl p-6 text-white shadow-lg shadow-indigo-100 relative overflow-hidden">
              <div class="relative z-10">
                <i data-feather="info" class="w-8 h-8 opacity-60 mb-4"></i>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
                  운영 상태 변경은 이름 수정과 분리되어 처리됩니다. 상태 변경 시 사용자 노출 여부에 바로 영향을 줄 수 있으니 신중하게 진행하세요.
                </p>
              </div>
              <i data-feather="shield" class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 opacity-10"></i>
            </div>
          </aside>

          <section class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
            <form method="post" action="{{model.updateAction}}" class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
              <input type="hidden" name="{{_csrf.parameterName}}" value="{{_csrf.token}}">
              <input type="hidden" name="departmentId" value="{{model.departmentId}}">

              <div class="p-6 border-b border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/60 flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <i data-feather="edit-3" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h2 class="font-bold text-slate-800">기본 정보 수정</h2>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">진료과명은 이 화면에서 바로 수정할 수 있습니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="p-8 space-y-6">
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <label for="department-name" class="block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
                    진료과명 <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                  </label>
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    id="department-name"
                    name="name"
                    value="{{model.name}}"
                    required
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:bg-white focus:ring-4 focus:ring-indigo-500/10 focus:border-indigo-500 outline-none transition-all text-slate-800 font-medium"
                    placeholder="진료과명을 입력하세요"
                  >
                </div>

                <div class="pt-2 flex items-center justify-end gap-3">
                  <a
                    href="/admin/department/list"
                    class="px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-xl transition-colors"
                  >
                    목록으로
                  </a>

                  <button
                    type="submit"
                    class="px-8 py-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-700 shadow-lg shadow-indigo-200 transition-all flex items-center gap-2"
                  >
                    <i data-feather="save" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    이름 수정
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </form>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6 border-b border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/60 flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <i data-feather="power" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h2 class="font-bold text-slate-800">상태 관리</h2>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">운영 상태는 이름 수정과 분리해 안전하게 변경합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6">
                <div class="max-w-md">
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1">운영 상태 변경</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                    현재 상태는 <span class="font-semibold text-slate-700">{{model.activeText}}</span>입니다.
                    상태 전이 버튼은 현재 상태에 따라 하나만 노출됩니다.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  {{#model.deactivatable}}
                    <form method="post" action="{{model.deactivateAction}}" class="inline-block">
                      <input type="hidden" name="{{_csrf.parameterName}}" value="{{_csrf.token}}">
                      <input type="hidden" name="departmentId" value="{{model.departmentId}}">
                      <button
                        type="submit"
                        class="px-6 py-3 bg-red-50 text-red-600 text-sm font-bold rounded-xl border border-red-100 hover:bg-red-100 transition-all flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap"
                      >
                        <i data-feather="pause-circle" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                        진료과 비활성화
                      </button>
                    </form>
                  {{/model.deactivatable}}

                  {{#model.activatable}}
                    <form method="post" action="{{model.activateAction}}" class="inline-block">
                      <input type="hidden" name="{{_csrf.parameterName}}" value="{{_csrf.token}}">
                      <input type="hidden" name="departmentId" value="{{model.departmentId}}">
                      <button
                        type="submit"
                        class="px-6 py-3 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 text-sm font-bold rounded-xl border border-indigo-100 hover:bg-indigo-100 transition-all flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap"
                      >
                        <i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                        진료과 활성화
                      </button>
                    </form>
                  {{/model.activatable}}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    {{> common/footer-staff}}
  </div>

  <script>
    feather.replace();
  </script>
</body>
</html>